text: Kim Sang-eun (; born August 6, 1978), known professionally as Lee Ji-ah, is an actress from South Korea. She is famous for her roles in the television series The Legend (2007), Beethoven Virus (2008), Athena: Goddess of War (2010), Me Too, Flower!
